========
vchkuser
========

:Author: `Benedikt BÃ¶hm <bb@xnull.de>`_
:Version: 0.1
:Web: http://bb.xnull.de/projects/vchkuser/
:Source: http://git.xnull.de/gitweb/?p=vchkuser.git
:Download: http://bb.xnull.de/projects/vchkuser/dist/

The vchkuser qmail-spp plugin checks for recipient existence with vpopmail. It
is based on a script by Werner Maier (http://www.maiers.de/qmail/art38,71.html)


Installation
============

to install vchkuser and the suid wrapper do the following as root:
::

  gcc -o vchkuser vchkuser.c
  mv vchkuser vchkuser.sh /var/qmail/plugins/
  chmod +s /var/qmail/plugins/vchkuser


Configuration
=============

In the ``[rcpt]`` section of ``/var/qmail/control/smtpplugins`` add the following:
::

  plugins/vchkuser

Edit ``/var/qmail/plugins/vchkuser.sh`` to change vpopmail's home or logging options.
